HEADWORD: Grogran
<hw>Grog"ran</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>gros-grain</ets>, lit., gros-grain,
of a coarse texture. See <er>Gross</er>, and <er>Grain</er> a kernel,
and cf. <er>Grog</er>.]</ety> <def>A coarse stuff made of silk and
mohair, or of coarse silk.</def>⟦br⟧
